      "text": "③ Claude AI Orchestrator starts agentic tool loop\n       a.  get_market_data      → ticker + OHLCV candles (6 timeframes)\n       b.  analyze_news         → EmotionScore from Claude AI\n       c.  get_technicals       → RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, EMA, trend\n       d.  get_portfolio_state  → balance, positions, daily P&L",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "③ Claude AI Orchestrator starts agentic tool loop\n       a.  get_market_data      → ticker + OHLCV candles (6 timeframes)\n       b.  analyze_news         → EmotionScore from Claude AI\n       c.  get_technicals       → RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, EMA, trend\n       d.  get_portfolio_state  → balance, positions, daily P&L"
